name.en: Diabell, Fiendess of the White Woods
name.ja: <ruby>白<rt>しろ</rt></ruby>き<ruby>森<rt>もり</rt></ruby>の<ruby>妖<rt>よう</rt></ruby><ruby>魔<rt>ま</rt></ruby>ディアベル

text.en:
1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters
If this card is Synchro Summoned using a Tuner Synchro Monster as material: You can target 1 Spell/Trap in your GY; add it to your hand. When your opponent activates a card or effect (Quick Effect): You can send 1 Spell/Trap from your hand or field to the GY; Special Summon 1 Level 7 or lower Tuner Synchro Monster from your Extra Deck, GY, or banishment. You can only use each effect of "Diabell, Fiendess of the White Woods" once per turn.
